er’s hobby is to watch movies.</p></div>		<! Question 3>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>3. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;母はうたをうたう&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('1',this.value,2)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>の</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>は</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>も</OPTION>    <OPTION value='4'>none</OPTION>	</SELECT>が好きです。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;My mother likes to sing songs.</p></div>	<! Question 4>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>4. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;X：どこへ行きましょうか。<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;　Y：どこ&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,3)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>も</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>か</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>でも</OPTION>	</SELECT>、いいですよ。 	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;X: Where shall we go?<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Y: Any place is fine with me.</p></div>		<! Question 5>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>5. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;チンさんは、しゃしん&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,4)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>も</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>で</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>を</OPTION>	</SELECT>とっている人です。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Chin-san is the person who is taking photos.</p></div>	<! Question 6>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>6. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;音楽が好き&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('1',this.value,5)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>な</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>の</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>こと</OPTION>    <OPTION value='4'>none</OPTION>	</SELECT>人は、だれですか。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The person who likes music, who is it?</p></div>		<! Question 7>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>7. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;スポーツは、見るのとするのとどちらの&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('2',this.value,6)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>こと</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>ほう</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>でも</OPTION>	</SELECT>が好きですか。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;As for sports, which do you prefer? To watch or to do?</p></div>	<! Question 8>	<div class="questionLineOdd">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;見る&nbsp;&nbsp;	 <SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,7)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>の</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>こと</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>none</OPTION>	</SELECT>ほうが好きです。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I prefer to watch.</p></div>	                    	<! Question 9>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>8. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;町田さんはピアノ&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('1',this.value,8)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>を</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>が</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>で</OPTION>	</SELECT>ひくこと &nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('2',this.value,9)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>を</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>が</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>で</OPTION>	</SELECT>できます。	<div class="symbols">    <IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif">    <IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif">    </div>	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Machida-san is able to play piano.</p></div>                  	<! Question 10>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>9. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;今しゅうのしゅうまつ、ともだち&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('1',this.value,10)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>が</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>を</OPTION>	</SELECT>あえます。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;This weekend I can see my friend.</p></div>	 	<! Question 11>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>10. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;カーチスさんは、かんじが上手&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('2',this.value,11)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>で</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>も</OPTION>	</SELECT>書けます。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Cutis can write kanji skillfully.</p></div>	<! Question 12>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>11. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;明日&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,12)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>へ</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>none</OPTION>	</SELECT>姉はパーティー&nbsp;&nbsp; 	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('1',this.value,13)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>へ</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>none</OPTION>	</SELECT>来られません。	<div class="symbols">    <IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif">    <IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif">    </div>	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;My older sister will not be able to come to the party tomorrow.</p></div>		<! Question 13>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>12.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;そぼは、りょうり&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,14)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>を</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>で </OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>が</OPTION>	</SELECT>とくいです。	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;My grandmother is good at and likes cooking.</p>	</div>		<! Question 14>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>13. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;土曜日&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,15)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>で</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>も</OPTION>	</SELECT>日曜日 &nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,16)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>で</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>も</OPTION>	</SELECT>はたらけます。	<div class="symbols">    <IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif">    <IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif">    </div>	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I can work both on Saturday and on Sunday.</p></div>	<! Question 15>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>14. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;プールはおよぐ&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,17)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>の</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>こと</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>none</OPTION>	</SELECT>ところです。 	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The pool is the place that people swim at.</p></div>		<! Question 16>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>15. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;冬&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('1',this.value,18)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>に</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>へ</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>none</OPTION>	</SELECT>なりました。&nbsp;&nbsp;	<SELECT name="answer" size=1 onChange="checkAnswer('3',this.value,19)">	<OPTION value='0'> -- </OPTION>	<OPTION value='1'>寒いに</OPTION>	<OPTION value='2'>寒くて</OPTION>	<OPTION value='3'>寒く</OPTION>	</SELECT>なりましたね。	<div class="symbols">    <IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif">    <IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif">    </div>	<p class="translationLine">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;It’s winter now. It has gotten cold.</p></div>			</FORM><div id="score"></div><div><table class="optionBox"><tr>	<td><BUTTON onClick="checkAnswers()">Check Answers</BUTTON></td>	<td><BUTTON onClick="resetValues()">Reset Values</BUTTON></td></tr></table></div></div></body></html>